{"tid":696558,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三重父子互砍　99歲老父削斷59歲子食指","createTime":"2018-06-10T08:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T08:34:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba29d1cb9e6f6546b9d1d6fb7105b5468ae0442","tid":696558,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:07:05.000Z","msg":"新北市三重一對陳姓父子，今天中午12時許在家中突然發生口角，雙方激烈爭吵後竟持刀互砍；高齡已99歲的陳父揮刀猛砍59歲的兒子，造成兒子頭部、手部多處刀傷，食指還因此遭削斷，痛的大叫救命。陳父手腕上也被兒子劃傷造成4公分的刀傷，鄰居聽聞救命聲趕緊報警。<br />\n警消獲報到場，研判情況緊急，立刻破門進入救援，替手指遭砍斷的陳子包紮止血後送往醫院急救，所幸並無生命危險，而陳父也被送往醫院治療。警方將待雙方傷勢穩定後再進行偵訊，以釐清這起父子相殘的行兇動機。（突發中心黃子騰／新北報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180610/1370708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180610%2F1370708&d=7PDsvg2KrTbVn4TX6Xn7OTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=0570dbec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180610%2F1370708&h=60b14992\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180610/1370708</a>"},{"pid":"36ca4da3a5ee388a78b56d01781369486d9eaab2","tid":696558,"uid":58140,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"我仲係度諗咩三重父子<br />\n原來三重係一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82fb096ebabaa2644bb3c134045d35472035a6e","tid":696558,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"99歲都打唔贏？唔撚係呀。"},{"pid":"183158140f87f9b2fe740438823237e2df9bbe5f","tid":696558,"uid":120715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"真正嘅格劍"},{"pid":"c9f20a9b2b4bfe4b699e09719c59d99276210c70","tid":696558,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"樓豬有冇咁鍾意PO台灣新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c